               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The <ph platform="PXP PxW" class="- topic/ph ">UPS</ph>
                        <ph platform="WxW" class="- topic/ph ">Inverter</ph>
                        <ph platform="SDC" class="- topic/ph ">Charger</ph>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Inside the system.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The network monitoring system</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The parts of the network monitoring system placed in the low voltage
section<ph platform="SDC" class="- topic/ph "> (for SDC systems the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A091</b> is not
located in the low voltage section.)</ph>.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b platform="PxW WxW SDC" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A070</b>
                        <b platform="PXP" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A102</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph platform="PxW WxW SDC" class="- topic/ph ">Controller board</ph>
                        <ph platform="PXP" class="- topic/ph ">Controller box</ph>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The <ph platform="PxW WxW SDC" class="- topic/ph ">controller board</ph>
                        <ph platform="PXP" class="- topic/ph ">controller box</ph> sends information and status changes in the system
to the <ph platform="PXP PxW WxW" class="- topic/ph ">communication interface</ph>
                        <ph platform="SDC" class="- topic/ph ">external connection board</ph>.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b platform="PxW WxW" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A076</b>
                        <b platform="SDC" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A025</b>
                        <b platform="PXP" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A830</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p platform="PXP PxW WxW" class="- topic/p ">Communication interface</p>
                     <p platform="SDC" class="- topic/p ">External connection board</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p platform="PxW WxW SDC" class="- topic/p ">Extends the signal from the controller board
and to the smart slot translator.</p>
                     <p platform="PXP" class="- topic/p ">Connects directly
to the network management cards.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row platform="PxW WxW SDC" class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b platform="PxW WxW SDC" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A091</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Smart slot translator</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Converts the signal from the controller board to another type of
protocol. Allows for local connection to the NMC.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b platform="PxW WxW SDC" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A092</b>
                        <b platform="PXP" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A842</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Network management card (NMC)</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Offers secure local and/or remote monitoring of Reality systems.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b platform="PxW WxW SDC" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A093</b>
                        <b platform="PXP" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">A832</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Options slot</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">An additional slot for an optional second NMC card that can be used
for:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Additional available ports with two NMCs.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">A second NMC with different settings.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Redundant network communication.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Two digital inputs.</p>
                           </li>
                        </ul>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
